OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds
OL,6,Fand sunny spells to end the day.
OL,7,FHowever, cloud will increase from the
OL,8,Fwest overnight, with a little light
OL,9,Frain or showers possible over western
OL,10,Fhills. A slightly milder night under
OL,11,Fthe blanket of cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA rather cloudy start with a
OL,14,Flittle light rain in the west. Cloud
OL,15,Fthen tending to break up allowing
OL,16,Fshowers to develop, these heavy at
OL,17,Ftimes, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
